🧾 指令支援

save_holdings

用於儲存 OCR 後的持股資料。

{
  "command": "save_holdings",
  "args": {
    "source": "ocr",
    "data": [
      {
        "symbol": "2330.TW",
        "name": "台積電",
        "shares": 1000,
        "avg_cost": 580.0,
        "currency": "TWD",
        "retrieved_at": "2025-07-16T12:00:00+08:00"
      }
    ]
  }
}


⸻

get_holdings

查詢持股資訊。來源可為：
	•	"ocr"：查詢已儲存的 JSON（可指定 ID）
	•	"broker"：查詢指定券商 API

{
  "command": "get_holdings",
  "args": {
    "source": "broker",
    "broker": "fubon"
  }
}

或查詢 OCR 儲存紀錄：

{
  "command": "get_holdings",
  "args": {
    "source": "ocr",
    "id": "ocr_20250716_01"
  }
}


